# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# PReminder — Environment Variables
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in the values.
# The app validates all variables at startup — see src/lib/env.ts
#
# NEVER commit .env.local or .env to version control!
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Core ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Base URL of your app (no trailing slash)
NEXTAUTH_URL=http://localhost:3000

# Random secret for signing session JWTs
# Generate: openssl rand -base64 32
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=

# ── GitHub OAuth ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Create at: https://github.com/settings/developers → OAuth Apps
# Callback URL: {NEXTAUTH_URL}/api/auth/callback/github
GITHUB_CLIENT_ID=
GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET=

# Your GitHub organization slug (e.g., "my-company")
GITHUB_ORG=

# ── Database ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PostgreSQL connection string
# Supabase: postgresql://postgres.[ref]:[pass]@aws-0-[region].pooler.supabase.com:6543/postgres
# Local: postgresql://preminder:preminder@localhost:5432/preminder?schema=public
# Azure: postgresql://[user]:[pass]@[host].postgres.database.azure.com:5432/preminder?sslmode=require
DATABASE_URL=

# ── Encryption ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Key for encrypting webhook URLs and tokens stored in DB
# Generate: openssl rand -hex 32 (produces 64 hex characters)
ENCRYPTION_KEY=

# ── Microsoft Graph API (Optional) ───────────────────────────
# Required for automated email sending via Outlook.
# Create at: https://portal.azure.com → Azure AD → App registrations
# Permissions needed: Mail.Send (delegated), User.Read (delegated)
AZURE_AD_CLIENT_ID=
AZURE_AD_CLIENT_SECRET=
AZURE_AD_TENANT_ID=

# ── Feature Flags ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Enable/disable features. NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix exposes to browser.

# Enable Graph API email (requires Azure AD credentials above)
NEXT_PUBLIC_ENABLE_GRAPH_EMAIL=false

# Enable desktop notifications (Web Notifications API)
NEXT_PUBLIC_ENABLE_DESKTOP_NOTIFICATIONS=true

# ── Docker Build (set only when building Docker image) ────────
# When true, uses Next.js standalone output mode
# DOCKER_BUILD=true

# ── Development Only ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Uncomment for verbose Prisma query logging
# PRISMA_LOG_LEVEL=query
